dc_title_s: Map of Ann Arbor showing campus and buildings of the University of Michigan prepared by Wickes Brothers.
dc_description_s: Concentric radii drawn every quarter-mile. Verso: Key to University and other buildings, description of University buildings, and a bird's-eye view of the campus. MiU copy mounted on chartex. 1 map.: 44 x 36 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
